This was the worst week
of your life, Tina?

20:31.051 --> 20:33.653
You got to crash a car
and burn down a house!

20:33.687 --> 20:35.321
I got to do nothing!

20:35.356 --> 20:37.690
Fine. Here, Louise,
you can break this plate.

20:37.725 --> 20:38.341
Ah!

20:38.375 --> 20:39.776
No fair!
I want one!

20:39.810 --> 20:41.094
Yeah!

20:41.128 --> 20:42.862
That felt good.
I want another one!

20:42.896 --> 20:44.180
No, that's it.

20:44.214 --> 20:45.765
Here, give me one!
Stop!

20:45.799 --> 20:46.799
Lin, what are you doing?

20:46.834 --> 20:48.668
What? They're...
I hate these plates.

20:48.702 --> 20:50.136
Stop breaking plates! Lin!

20:50.170 --> 20:51.371
Ah!

20:51.405 --> 20:52.742
- Ah-ha-ha, it's fun.
- Smash!

20:52.862 --> 20:55.751
